{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/add-color-swatches-to-the-product-page-no-apps","result":{"pageContext":{"id":3804,"date":"2024-03-18T13:09:27","date_gmt":"2024-03-18T13:09:27","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=3804"},"modified":"2024-03-18T13:37:24","modified_gmt":"2024-03-18T13:37:24","slug":"add-color-swatches-to-the-product-page-no-apps","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/add-color-swatches-to-the-product-page-no-apps/","title":{"rendered":"Add color swatches to the product page [NO apps]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Ever wished your Shopify free theme could have these beautiful, instant-loading color swatches? While there are apps that achieve this functionality, not only do they come with monthly fees, but they also take a toll on your website&#8217;s speed by injecting bloated code, thus prejudicing its performance and causing longer loading times.<br><br>With our copy/paste code, you&#8217;ll be able to replace all of your variant pills with actual colors without relying on any third parties. This will ensure your website can make good use of improved UX, with code being loaded as fast as technically possible.<br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/products/colorful-bean-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live demo of the end result</a>. <br><br>This live demo also uses our <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/dawn-theme-slider-pro\">Slider Pro with Vertical Thumbnail</a>, an improved Slider copy/paste code compatible with all Shopify&#8217;s free themes. <br><br>Without further ado, let&#8217;s dive in.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"NoticeBox NoticeBox--info\"><p>This tutorial is compatible only with Shopify&#8217;s official free themes: <b>Dawn, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Spotlight, Publisher, Sense &amp; Craft.</b></p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-creating-the-section-code\">Creating the section code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>From your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>3 dots </strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the sections folder and click on &#8220;Add a new section&#8221;. Name it exactly:<br><br><strong>ezfy-color-variants</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1476\" height=\"849\" class=\"wp-image-3810\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/t2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/t2.jpg 1476w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/t2-850x489.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/t2-1200x690.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/t2-768x442.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1476px) 100vw, 1476px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following code inside and save:<br><br>[gist]5d35a5b9416f642a600b66f4854cae3e[gist]</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-creating-the-css-code\">Creating the CSS code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Find&nbsp;the <strong>snippets </strong>folder and click on &#8220;Add a new snippet&#8221;.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Name it exactly:<br><br><strong>ezfy-color-variants-css</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1453\" height=\"790\" class=\"wp-image-3820\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z1.jpg 1453w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z1-850x462.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z1-1200x652.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z1-768x418.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1453px) 100vw, 1453px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following code inside this file and save.<br><br>[gist]6a1a0a02fabb4192252570f8bb01f8e0[gist]<br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"637\" height=\"486\" class=\"wp-image-1300\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/theme-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><br>5. Press CTRL + F (CMD + F on Mac) to trigger the search box and find:<br><br><strong>&lt;/head</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1198\" height=\"839\" class=\"wp-image-3822\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z2.jpg 1198w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z2-850x595.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z2-768x538.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1198px) 100vw, 1198px\" /><br><br>6. Paste the following code <strong>above</strong> the line you found:<br><br><strong>{% render &#8216;ezfy-badges-color&#8217; %}</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1078\" height=\"860\" class=\"wp-image-3824\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z3.jpg 1078w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z3-850x678.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z3-768x613.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1078px) 100vw, 1078px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-adding-colors-in-the-customize-page\">Adding colors in the customize page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Click on &#8220;3 dots > customize theme&#8221;, on the top left.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1382\" height=\"759\" class=\"wp-image-3829\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z4.jpg 1382w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z4-850x467.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z4-1200x659.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z4-768x422.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1382px) 100vw, 1382px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>At the top, click on &#8220;Products > default products&#8221;.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1345\" height=\"864\" class=\"wp-image-3831\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z5.jpg 1345w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z5-850x546.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z5-1200x771.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z5-768x493.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1345px) 100vw, 1345px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1307\" height=\"839\" class=\"wp-image-3833\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z6.jpg 1307w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z6-850x546.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z6-1200x770.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z6-768x493.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1307px) 100vw, 1307px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now add the <strong>EZFY Variant Colors</strong> section.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1291\" height=\"875\" class=\"wp-image-3835\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z7.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z7.jpg 1291w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z7-850x576.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z7-1200x813.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z7-768x521.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1291px) 100vw, 1291px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-how-to-customize-the-colors\">How to customize the colors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you have added the EZFY Variant Colors section, it&#8217;s very simple to add colors:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Click on &#8220;add block&#8221; and choose what type of color you&#8217;d like to add. You can choose between:<br>1. a HEX color<br>2. two HEX colors that will show up 50%/50% (multicolor)<br>3. Image<br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>In this example, let&#8217;s customize the &#8220;black &amp; gray&#8221; variant. <br><br>Since it&#8217;s two colors, we can choose the &#8220;multicolor&#8221; block and add the exact same name of the variant. Once you click on the &#8220;save&#8221; button, the changes will take place.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1559\" height=\"650\" class=\"wp-image-3839\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9.jpg 1559w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9-850x354.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9-1200x500.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9-768x320.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z9-1536x640.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1559px) 100vw, 1559px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1778\" height=\"655\" class=\"wp-image-3841\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11.jpg 1778w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11-850x313.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11-1200x442.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11-768x283.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/z11-1536x566.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1778px) 100vw, 1778px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>The process is the same for all other blocks. Add the variant name, and choose its respective color or image. Simple!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Colors that are not added to the &#8220;variants&#8221; block will show up as text as they do by default.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in. They work with &#8220;Dawn&#8221; plus all Shopify&#8217;s free themes (Craft, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Spotlight, Publisher &amp; Sense):<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Replace your products&#8217; color names with actual colors. Free and simple, no apps.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3848,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,776,773,663,649,652,646,660],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dawn-badges-5-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dawn-badges-5-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dawn-badges-5-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","origin theme","publisher theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Taste theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dawn-badges-5.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/3804"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=3804"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/3804/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3856,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/3804/revisions/3856"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/3848"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=3804"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categori